{"tid":1992512,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞和之役有冇打算透過鄭若驊嘅「網上爭議解決計劃」調解/仲裁？","createTime":"2020-04-28T07:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T15:44:57.000Z","uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c654adab561995f8066dc699b4a1ee61ffe6e62","tid":1992512,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:45:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202004/27/P2020042700568.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202004%2F27%2FP2020042700568.htm&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=35fcef76\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202004/27/P2020042700568.htm</a><br />\n<blockquote><em>防疫抗疫支援措施<br />\n <br />\n  第二項措施為推出新型冠狀病毒網上爭議解決計劃。考慮到企業，尤其是中小企及微中小企，及公眾在疫情下就爭議解決方面的需求，律政司將透過一邦國際網上仲調中心有限公司於六月推出快速及具成本效益的網上爭議解決計劃，讓爭端雙方通過網上平台進行談判、調解及仲裁以解決爭議。該計劃的管轄範圍是：（1）因新型冠狀病毒病爆發而直接或間接地引起或有關的糾紛；（2）當事人其中一方為香港居民或公司；及（3）索償金額少於50萬港元。<span style=\"color: red;\">在此計劃下，爭端雙方只需各付200港元作登記費用，而調解員及仲裁員的費用將由政府支付。</span><br />\n <br />\n  網上爭議解決計劃能防止加劇衝突，紓緩過去數月法院因一般延期而積壓的民事索償案件量，並有助建立社會和諧。同時，該計劃能為調解員和仲裁員（包括他們的學徒）帶來就業機會和學習如何處理線上案件，讓他們可於社交隔離措施下仍然處理案件，並符合發展網上爭議解決服務的全球趨勢，例如《亞太經合組織網上爭議解決的合作框架》及聯合國貿法委就法律科技的工作，有助增強香港的法律科技能力。</em></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過有啲貴，瑞和街體育館活動室(112平方米)星期日場租都只係每小時57元......<br />\n<blockquote>星期日及公眾假期任何時段<br />\n100平方米或以上的活動室/ 舞蹈室<br />\n有空氣調節 每小時57元</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/tc/leisurelink/index/ls_booking_charges_urban.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fleisurelink%2Findex%2Fls_booking_charges_urban.html&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=ca10f9c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/tc/leisurelink/index/ls_booking_charges_urban.html</a><br />\n<blockquote>1個面積為112平方米的活動室，可供進行舞蹈、武術、瑜伽、跆拳道、柔道等(配套設施:牆鏡、扶槓、音響設備和地墊)</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/clpss/tc/webApp/Facility/Details.do?fid=1006&amp;did=6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcsd.gov.hk%2Fclpss%2Ftc%2FwebApp%2FFacility%2FDetails.do%3Ffid%3D1006%26did%3D6&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=631d24e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/clpss/tc/webApp/Facility/Details.do?fid=1006&amp;did=6</a><br />\n不過食炒場師價就另計了........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5042023b57a04712317ee109f78e39c871e55a73","tid":1992512,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:46:39.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ddb47c3a9fec9ee57de7c1551eb83aeee406d998","tid":1992512,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5042023b57a04712317ee109f78e39c871e55a73","tid":1992512,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:46:39.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:47:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"00e757d93b9cf6ffadbcc007a13c5e82e8a93cbf","tid":1992512,"uid":268516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:55:59.000Z","msg":"網上調解過程有人亂入播AV<br />\n然後大家口味一致咁就做番朋友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4139cb3c9d088b8b6ee39acedf961a8fae3a1c12","tid":1992512,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"00e757d93b9cf6ffadbcc007a13c5e82e8a93cbf","tid":1992512,"uid":268516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:55:59.000Z","msg":"網上調解過程有人亂入播AV<br />\n然後大家口味一致咁就做番朋友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/001/505/041/eb9.jpg